modName: Expanded Towns and Cities and Marshlands Patch
summary: A patch between the Immersive Environments Project: Marshlands and Expanded Towns and Cities version 14.3.1 mod.
descriptionHtml:
Originally created for TeaMistress of r/skyrimmods, this patch serves to remove clipping trees from Morthal where they would be added by either Expanded Towns and Cities or else Immersive Environments Project: Marshlands. Works for ETaC version 14.3.1, and IEP Marshlands version 1.3

ETaC available [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13608]here[/url]


IEP Marshlands available [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30787]here[/url]
author: SkeeverBrain aka Erenna
